{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01UGwaChve3TxWa2xUoaCsoc","type":"tool_result","content":"/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/FAQ.md:51:Further, rpm-ostree supports package layering and overrides - these will also be preserved by the MCO (currently).  Although note that there is no current mechanism to trigger a MCO-coordinated drain/reboot, which is particularly relevant for `rpm-ostree install/override` changes.\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/FAQ.md:104:or `rpm-ostree install` etc.) won't have that repository enabled.\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-troubleshooting.md:65:        ostree container commit\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-troubleshooting.md:73:FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/UsingLayering.md:60:RUN rpm-ostree install libreswan && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/UsingLayering.md:62:    ostree container commit && rm /etc/yum.repos.d/redhat.repo\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/UsingLayering.md:77:RUN rpm-ostree install http://mirror.centos.org/centos/8-stream/AppStream/x86_64/os/Packages/ltrace-0.7.91-28.el8.x86_64.rpm && rpm-ostree cleanup -m\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:136:FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:137:RUN rpm-ostree install tree && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:138:    ostree container commit\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:145:- One must use the configs image target (`FROM configs AS final`) to\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:208:FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:209:RUN rpm-ostree install tree && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:210:    ostree container commit\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:262:          FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:263:          RUN rpm-ostree install tree && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/docs/onclusterlayering-quickstart.md:264:            ostree container commit\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/bootstrap/testdata/bootstrap/layered-worker.machineosconfig.yaml:20:      FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/bootstrap/testdata/bootstrap/layered-worker.machineosconfig.yaml:21:      RUN rpm-ostree install httpd && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/bootstrap/testdata/bootstrap/layered-worker.machineosconfig.yaml:22:        ostree container commit\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/osbuildcontroller_test.go:87:\t\tapiMosc := testhelpers.SetContainerfileContentsOnMachineOSConfig(ctx, t, mcfgclient, mosc, \"FROM configs AS final\\nRUN echo 'helloworld' > /etc/helloworld\")\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/osbuildcontroller_test.go:188:\tsecondMosc, secondMosb := createNewMachineOSBuildViaConfigChange(firstMosc, \"FROM configs AS final\\nRUN echo 'hello' > /etc/hello\")\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/osbuildcontroller_test.go:194:\tthirdMosc, thirdMosb := createNewMachineOSBuildViaConfigChange(firstMosc, \"FROM configs AS final\\nRUN echo 'helloworld' > /etc/helloworld\")\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/osbuildcontroller_test.go:240:\t\tnewMosc := testhelpers.SetContainerfileContentsOnMachineOSConfig(ctx, t, mcfgclient, mosc, \"FROM configs AS final\\nRUN echo 'helloworld' > /etc/helloworld\")\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/osbuildcontroller_test.go:313:\t\t\tapiMosc := testhelpers.SetContainerfileContentsOnMachineOSConfig(ctx, t, mcfgclient, mosc, \"FROM configs AS final\"+fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", i))\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/buildrequest/buildrequest_test.go:292:\tcontainerfileContents := `FROM configs AS final\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/buildrequest/buildrequest_test.go:293:RUN rpm-ostree install && \\\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/buildrequest/buildrequest_test.go:294:\tostree container commit`\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/pkg/controller/build/fixtures/objects.go:96:\t\tWithContainerfile(mcfgv1.NoArch, \"FROM configs AS final\\n\\nRUN echo 'hi' > /etc/hi\")\n/home/jsuri/random-testing/prashanth-help/machine-config-operator/test/e2e-1of2/mcd_test.go:1207:\tt.Logf(\"Executing rpm-ostree install command on node %s\", node.Name)","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_014NA5Hm4ucczaQabTwCT8iW","session_id":"e75a21bc-7faa-413c-8450-02eaf032edac","uuid":"58f70e5c-63a9-4b93-8c15-0311a6a1583d","timestamp":"2026-06-22T21:08:07.064Z","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Search for MachineOSConfig and on-cluster layering docs"}
